# Superdesign Landing Page

A sophisticated, editorial-style landing page for Superdesign, an autonomous AI design agent. This component focuses on structural clarity, minimalist aesthetics, and advanced scroll-triggered interactions.

## Dependencies
- `react`: ^18.2.0
- `framer-motion`: ^11.0.8 (for sophisticated animations)
- `lucide-react`: ^0.344.0 (for iconography)
- `clsx` & `tailwind-merge`: (for clean Tailwind class management)

